    "excerpt": "This is a blessing which I originally wrote while working at the Leo Baeck Education Center, Haifa, for the International Human Rights day, December 10, 2012. It is based on the 4th of the Seven Blessings in the Jewish wedding ceremony, with additional quotes from our tradition. This blessing is included in Tfilat HaAdam prayer book, 2021. . . .",
    "content": "<div class=\"english\" lang=\"en\" style=\"font-size: 1.2em;\">\nThis is a blessing which I originally wrote while working at the Leo Baeck Education Center, Haifa, for the International Human Rights Day, December 10, 2012. It is based on the 4th of the Seven Blessings in the Jewish wedding ceremony, with additional quotes from our tradition. This blessing is included in Tfilat HaAdam prayer book, 2021.\n</div>\n<hr />\n\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" class=\"draggable toggleable-table\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th id=\"x\" style=\"text-align: right;\">Source (Hebrew)</th>\n<th style=\"text-align: left;\">Translation (English)</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"he\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nבָּרוּךְ אַתָּה<br />\nה׳ אֱלֹהֵינוּ<br />\nמֶלֶךְ הָעוֹלָם,<br />\nאֲשֶׁר יָצַר אֶת הָאָדָם בְּצַלְמוֹ,<br />\nבְּצֶלֶם דְּמוּת תַּבְנִיתוֹ,<br />\nזָכָר וּנְקֵבָה בְּרָאָם<br />\nוַיְבָרֶךְ אֹתָם<br />\nוַיִּקְרָא אֶת שְׁמָם אָדָם.<br />\nלְלַמְּדֵנו שֶׁכׇּל נֶפֶשׁ<br />\nהִיא כְּעוֹלָם מָלֵא<br />\nוְכׇל נְשָׁמָה הִיא נֵר אֶלֹהִי,<br />\nמָקוֹר אֶחָד לְכֻלָּנוּ,<br />\nאֵל אֶחָד בְּרָאָנוּ,<br />\nאֵין פַּרְצוּפֵינוּ דּוֹמִים זֶה לָזֶה<br />\nוְאֵין דֵּעוֹתֵינוּ דּוֹמוֹת זֶוֹ לָזֶוֹ,<br />\nוְכׇל אַחַת וְאֶחָד נִבְרְאוּ בְּחוֹתָמוֹ.<br />\nבָּרוּךְ אַתָּה ה׳, יוֹצֵר הָאָדָם:\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"en\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nBlessed are you,<br />\nAdonai our God,<br />\nSovereign of the universe,<br />\nwho created Humanity in God&#8217;s image,<br />\n[in the image of the likeness of God&#8217;s pattern]&nbsp;<br />\nmale and female God created them,<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_1');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_1');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_1\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[1]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_1\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Genesis 1:27, Genesis 5:2.&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_1').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_1', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script>&nbsp;<br />\nblessed them<br />\nand called them Adam,<br />\nso we may learn that each soul<br />\nin an entire world,<br />\neach spirit is a divine candle,<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_2');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_2');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_2\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[2]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_2\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Proverbs 20:27.&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_2').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_2', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script>&nbsp;<br />\nwe all come from one source,<br />\nthe One God created us all,<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_3');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_3');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_3\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[3]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_3\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Malachi 2:10.&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_3').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_3', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script>&nbsp;<br />\nour faces are different<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_4');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_4');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_4\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[4]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_4\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Talmud Yerushalmi Berakhot 63b.&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_4').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_4', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script>&nbsp;<br />\nand our thoughts are different,<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_5');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_5');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_5\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[5]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_5\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Rav Quq, הראי״ה קוק, עין אי״ה על מסכת ברכות (Ayin Aya on Tractate Berakhot): ככל שנעמיק להתבונן במבנה האופי הפרטי של בני האדם, נתפלא יותר ויותר על השוני הרב הקיים ביניהם. שוני זה, מגזרת החכמה העליונה הוא בא. אילו היו כל בני האדם שווים זה לזה בהלך רוחם, לא היה כל אדם ואדם וכל חוג וחוג מושך לכיוונו בצורה קיצונית וקנאית כל־כך, ומתוך כך היה העולם נחסר דעות, כיוונים ורעיונות שונים ומפרים. (&#8220;The deeper we look into the structure of the private character of human beings, the more and more we will be surprised at the great difference between them. This difference derives from the region of Supernal Wisdom. If all human beings were equal to each other in their mentality, each and every person and group would not pull in their own direction in such an extreme and fanatical way, and as a result the world would be devoid of different and contravening opinions, directions, and ideas.&#8221; &#8211;translation, Aharon Varady)&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_5').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_5', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script>&nbsp;<br />\nyet each of us are stamped with God&#8217;s seal.<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_6');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_6');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_6\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[6]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_6\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Mishnah Sanhedrin 4.5.&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_6').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_6', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script>&nbsp;<br />\nBlessed are you, Adonai, creator of Humanity.<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_7');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_7');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_7\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[7]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_7\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Cf. the 4th of the Seven Wedding Blessings.&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_7').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_7', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<hr />\n<h3>Source(s)</h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_47767\" style=\"width: 242px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Birkat-Yotser-ha-Adam-for-International-Human-Rights-Day-Rabbi-Oded-Mazor-in-Siddur-Tefilat-ha-Adam-2021.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox-0\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47767\" src=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Birkat-Yotser-ha-Adam-for-International-Human-Rights-Day-Rabbi-Oded-Mazor-in-Siddur-Tefilat-ha-Adam-2021-232x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"232\" height=\"300\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-47767\" srcset=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Birkat-Yotser-ha-Adam-for-International-Human-Rights-Day-Rabbi-Oded-Mazor-in-Siddur-Tefilat-ha-Adam-2021-232x300.jpg 232w, https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Birkat-Yotser-ha-Adam-for-International-Human-Rights-Day-Rabbi-Oded-Mazor-in-Siddur-Tefilat-ha-Adam-2021.jpg 599w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 232px) 100vw, 232px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-47767\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Birkat Yotser ha-Adam for International Human Rights Day (Rabbi Oded Mazor in Siddur Tefilat ha-Adam 2021)</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"speaker-mute footnotes_reference_container\"> <div class=\"footnote_container_prepare\"><p><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_label pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_expand_collapse_reference_container__1();\">Notes</span><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_collapse_button\" style=\"display: none;\" onclick=\"footnote_expand_collapse_reference_container__1();\">[<a id=\"f